embeds.title: Massey Game Jam IV - Official End/Results
embeds.description: Thank you, everyone, for joining the jam, the Massey Game Jam team had an astonishing time! Hopefully, you had fun as well and made some games you are proud of!

fields.name: The Massey Game Jam IV Winners are:
fields.value:
:first_place: Paranormal Entities by AI Hack (4)
:second_place: A Walk In The Dark by Such_Nick (1)
:third_place: What is that? by MiniGloathj (3) 

All the judges had fun playing everyone's game and we hope to see you again! We've also posted the results in the <#743115835257913495> channel.
